comments: The program confirms that the "dip" in magnitude near a(15) is correct. - _R. J. Mathar_, Oct 31 2006
references: B. C. Berndt, Ramanujan's Notebooks Part III, Springer-Verlag, see p. 92, Eq. 2.5
maple: A051550 := proc(n) s := taylor( 1/(10+sqrt(36+x)),x=0,n+1) ; coeftayl(s,x=0,n) ; end: for n from 0 to 30 do printf("%a,",numer(A051550(n))) ; end: # _R. J. Mathar_, Oct 31 2006
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_
